Movie Insight App - Sample Test Cases
=====================================

1. Test Case: Valid IMDb ID
--------------------------
Input:
  IMDb ID: tt0111161 (The Shawshank Redemption)

Expected Output:
  - Movie details displayed: Title, Poster, Year, Genre, IMDb Rating, Director, Top Cast
  - AI Summary is generated (not empty)
  - Sentiment is Positive, Mixed, or Negative
  - Cast array contains up to 10 actors

---

2. Test Case: Invalid IMDb ID
-----------------------------
Input:
  IMDb ID: invalid123

Expected Output:
  - Display message: "No data found"
  - AI Summary shows: "AI summary unavailable"
  - Sentiment shows: "Unavailable"
  - Cast array is empty

---

3. Test Case: Empty IMDb ID
----------------------------
Input:
  IMDb ID: ""

Expected Output:
  - No request sent to backend
  - No movie card displayed
  - Optional: Show a validation message near input: "Please enter a valid IMDb ID"

---
